General Information

Swisse High Strength Chlorophyll+ is a premium quality formula containing organic chlorella, a green superfood that provides a natural source of vitamins and antioxidants to support energy metabolism, immune function and healthy skin.

Chlorella is a microscopic fresh water plant that is known to contain chlorophyll, vitamins B12 and C.

Energy Metabolism: Vitamins B12 and C support healthy energy metabolism and help reduce tiredness and fatigue.

Immune Support: Vitamins C and B12 support healthy immune function, helping to maintain a healthy immune system.

Healthy Skin: Vitamin C contributes to collagen formation, which helps maintain healthy skin function.

Antioxidant: Chlorella has antioxidant properties and is also a source of vitamin C, which helps protect cells from free radical damage.

Chlorophyll: The green pigment found in plants, chlorophyll is responsible for absorbing light from the sun and transforming it into energy.

Swisse High Strength Chlorophyll+ can be taken daily or as part of a healthy detox, which can be beneficial to support general health and wellbeing.

Swisse High Strength Chlorophyll+ provides a wholefood source of nutrients in a convenient, high strength dose.

Size: 200 Pack

Serving Size: 3.12 g (3 tablets)

Servings Per Pack: Approx. 66

Ingredients

Organic Chlorella powder 99%, silicon dioxide, magnesium stearate.

Directions

ADULT SERVE:

3 tablets daily.

The nutrients and benefits outlined can be obtained with 1 serve (3 tablets). You can take up to 3 serves daily if you choose to boost your nutrition further.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 30 degrees Celsius. Do not use if cap seal is broken.
